<p><strong>Condition Immunities</strong> blinded, deafened, frightened</p>

<p><strong>Senses</strong> blindsight 30 ft. (blind beyond this radius)</p>

<p><strong>Challenge</strong> 1/4 (50 XP)</p>

<p><strong><em>False Appearance.</em></strong> While the violet fungus remains motionless, it is indistinguishable from an ordinary fungus.</p>

<p><strong>Actions</strong></p>

<p><strong><em>Multiattack.</em></strong> The fungus makes 1d4 Rotting Touch attacks.</p>

<p><strong><em>Rotting Touch.</em></strong> Melee Weapon Attack: +2 to hit, reach 10 ft., one creature. Hit: 4 (1d8) necrotic damage.</p>

